overview: The Eye Center is the leading refractive practice in South Carolina, providing full service eye care and specializing in Refractive Surgery – Epi-Lasik, Thin Flap Lasik, AST, PRK CK, PRELEX, as well as Corneal Transplant and Cataract Surgery. Our eye physicians also treat eye emergencies, offer diabetic eye exams, follow and manage glaucoma, offer an in-house dry eye clinic, and conduct healthy eye checkups. Our Board Certified Ophthalmologists offer a superior level of experience and skill. Their compassion and dedication to our patients demonstrates their commitment to excellence. We offer the highest standards of sterile technique, stringent safety measures, superior service and state-of-the-art, FDA approved equipment.
